spells.description: Equip: Your spells have a chance to charge the device and request a Backfill Barrel near your target's location. Damaging the barrel causes it to explode, inflicting 691,694 Fire damage split between nearby enemies.

Use: Raise your signet to the Light, increasing your highest secondary stat by 7,278 for 20 sec. Your act inspires nearby signetbearers within your party, granting them 191 of the same stat for 20 sec. (2 Min Cooldown)
Use: Zap yourself for 273,079 Nature damage, gaining 16,473 Intellect for 15 sec. (45 Sec Cooldown)
